OL,4,CFather and son died after Usk water
OL,5,Cbuffalo attack
OL,6, A father was left with "unsurvivable
OL,7, injuries" after being trampled by a
OL,8, water buffalo that also killed his son
OL,9, at the family farm, an inquest heard.
OL,11,FJurors concluded that Ralph Jump, 57,
OL,12,Fdid not have a second person present or
OL,13,Fa place of safety when he entered the
OL,14,Ffield near Usk, in May 2020.
OL,16,FThey said these factors contributed to
OL,17,Fhim being attacked by the bull.
OL,19,FThe jury concluded that Mr Jump's son
OL,20,FPeter, 19, who went to his father's
OL,21,Faid, died as a result of misadventure.
